<main id="content" class="content"> <header> <h1 class="title">The Idol of Security</h1>
 <p class="subtitle" role="doc-subtitle">Dec 10, 2015 00:00</p>
</header> <p>
God of Peace,
</p>

 <p>
There was a time when <br></br>
we built idols of stone <br></br>
that separated us from you.
</p>

 <p>
Now, we are tempted <br></br>
to build new idols, <br></br>
walls that separate us <br></br>
from those created <br></br>
in your own image.
</p>

 <p>
Forgive us, Lord, <br></br>
for loving our own safety <br></br>
more than we love the gospel, <br></br>
and for sacrificing <br></br>
the dream of true peace <br></br>
on the altar of a <br></br>
false sense of security.
</p>

 <p>
 <i>Amen</i>
</p>


